{"tid":1903373,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"拗柴幾耐先好？","createTime":"2020-02-29T02:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T01:37:33.000Z","uid":66945,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"783414af4a194f6f2af05955854d33fd9660f088","tid":1903373,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:23:50.000Z","msg":"我1月5號落樓梯拗柴，拗完都仲行到20分鐘返屋企<br />\n夜晚有敷冰袋+抬高腳，不過就開始好痛行唔到+有腫腫地<br />\n第二朝又好似冇咩事行到路，係有少少痛。第三日完全係健步如飛<br />\n但係問題黎喇，到依加我都仲未可以將隻腳板向內屈， 會覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腳踝附近仲有輕微腫，上星期睇過一次跌打幫我用油推過+敷藥<br />\n咁耐都仲未屈得係咪唔正常?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c294aa085db00ef889bc187758979d6c888c18","tid":1903373,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:25:10.000Z","msg":"屈會痛嘅意思係: 做返拗柴咁屈會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f2f2b2ac90dd8c586cc6f9e0fc65081c9d6af3","tid":1903373,"uid":288048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"我之前都係跌咗樓梯拗柴 郁都郁唔到 我即晚去睇跌打 差唔多1,2個星期就好"},{"pid":"e6fa2a8fcc657851d3031eae2280109ebc0baa46","tid":1903373,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0f2f2b2ac90dd8c586cc6f9e0fc65081c9d6af3","tid":1903373,"uid":288048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"我之前都係跌咗樓梯拗柴 郁都郁唔到 我即晚去睇跌打 差唔多1,2個星期就好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"我夜晚先拗，跌打都閂哂門<br />\n第二日見自己行得就冇去睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你隻腳任屈都唔痛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e81d18de6d46bc2e317d7e24932bb0b1e8a19e5","tid":1903373,"uid":118945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T03:11:31.000Z","msg":"韌帶有無受傷？"},{"pid":"174ea66826e3c445e44a3c0a7c0642fd13be30c7","tid":1903373,"uid":6